    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing my pride and joy. This car is in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and made sure it was polished to perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see just how beautiful it is in person!",
