      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since the day I got it. It looks and drives just like it did when it first left the showroom. Not a scratch on it, and the interior is totally spotless. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to message me with any questions at all!",
